Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.42,0:00:09.00,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Distance: 250 m.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.37,0:00:11.91,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wind speed: 1.5.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.91,0:00:13.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Blowing from the right to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.52,0:00:15.00,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stop your breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.86,0:00:18.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Slowly... Quietly...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.73,0:00:27.50,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.91,0:00:31.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.39,0:00:45.96,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,With the passage of time, feeble humanity has evolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.96,0:00:49.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We traded our fangs for wisdom, and claws for tools in order to live longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.69,0:00:52.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:55.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We will be tested soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.06,0:01:00.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,When that time comes, you can't hesitate to pull the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:03.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.09,0:01:05.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll protect Suou.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.11,0:01:06.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.11,0:01:10.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That was the last time I saw his real smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.83,0:01:16.44,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,On the night of the Tokyo Explosion...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.56,0:01:18.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shion became a contractor
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.81,0:01:22.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,and as remuneration, his legs were paralyzed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.75,0:01:27.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I swore that I will protect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:32.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If this is a test, I'll pass it with flying colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.09,0:01:36.24,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I am his older sister after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.17,0:01:37.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:40.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:49.01,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,the true test had only just begun.
