Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:26.14,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shion Pavlichenko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:29.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hand over the meteor core.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:42.50,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A contractor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.74,0:04:02.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:04.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There are no enemies at the back of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.93,0:04:37.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:38.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.85,0:04:40.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Zdravstvuj. {Здравствуйте}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:42.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ni hao.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:45.50,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Guten Abend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:46.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:49.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Did you understand any one of those, cutie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:52.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.11,0:04:55.30,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so you speak Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:04:56.51,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:04:58.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like being rough, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:01.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be grateful if you be a good girl and come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:06.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Petya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:12.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.74,0:05:14.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Come, Petya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:22.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Such a naughty girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:42.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:43.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shion...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.38,0:05:56.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shion!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.55,0:05:57.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.05,0:06:20.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shizume-san! Hazuki-san! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.32,0:06:23.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Man, she was such a cutie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:25.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Playing hide and see—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.34,0:06:32.78,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Youko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:34.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:46.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's troublesome, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:49.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Having to kiss a guy to remunerate for using your pow—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.03,0:06:58.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Just removing the bad taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:09.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Even the contractor you were bragging about is in a body bag now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:11.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say, Debry?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:16.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like your subordinate wasn't even as useful as a bulletproof vest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:17.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Kozroff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.80,0:07:21.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how much it costs to train and supervise a contractor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.13,0:07:23.60,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What a useless investment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:25.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They're nothing more than monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.55,0:07:28.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They're useless either as soldiers or as weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:34.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I've ordered ME to erase the memories of the witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:36.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What about the professor's missing kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.86,0:07:38.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We're looking for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:42.14,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Broaden the area of the surveillance spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:45.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Put all the bodies into the ME squeezer...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.47,0:07:46.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,While they're still fresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:49.20,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course the creator, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.98,0:07:54.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,His brain is a precious asset of the state.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:22.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:25.40,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:27.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank heavens, you're home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:29.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Sasha! Let me hide for a whi—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.99,0:08:31.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:35.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,ME?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.82,0:08:46.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Tanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.83,0:08:50.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.69,0:09:05.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Nika Lobanov is in that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:07.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What did he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:09.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Theft and robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.67,0:09:14.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take him into custody. Please don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:51.15,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Suou?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.24,0:09:53.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Nika!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:56.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:09:57.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Who you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.98,0:09:59.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.63,0:10:09.38,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! Suou...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:11.00,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Suou?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:14.03,Title,,0,0,0,,Episode 2    The Fallen Star...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.97,0:10:27.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,"Thus, what enables the wise sovereign and the good general to strike and conquer,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:30.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,and achieve things beyond the reach of ordinary men, is foreknowledge." { from Sun Tzu's Art of War Chapter 13.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.49,0:10:36.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I've come to ask for your help again, Madame.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:41.30,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,One of my men stumbled upon something in the Far East.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.30,0:10:45.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The organization has finally made its move to obtain Izanagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:47.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you knew anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:54.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really grateful for business from the almighty CIA, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:11:01.00,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,"Foreknowledge cannot be elicited from spirits," Mr. Smith. {art of war chapter 13}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:05.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,"Know thy self, know thy enemy."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:07.50,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:15.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.08,0:11:21.72,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,When I called the people from class, they've all forgotten about Tanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:25.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And there was a fire at your house...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:28.24,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Is your father okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.24,0:11:29.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Suou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:41.40,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Darn, there's nothing useful here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:46.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Eat something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.47,0:11:48.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't eaten anything, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.05,0:12:04.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Suou...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:12.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough pondering!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.23,0:12:14.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,S-Suou?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:17.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm borrowing your desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.37,0:12:20.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:23.38,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's a badass anti-tank rifle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.74,0:12:28.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's scrap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:40.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait and see, old man in black!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.09,0:12:47.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,When I arrived, the professor was already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.39,0:12:48.91,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're telling the truth, I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.97,0:12:55.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Who were the people who intervened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.97,0:12:57.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We're investigating them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:13:00.51,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you know if we find anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.51,0:13:01.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There're so many missing pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.25,0:13:09.70,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The CIA specifically hired you to deal with these kinds of situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:12.14,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You'll obey us,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:14.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Black Grim Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:47.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wedding swindler.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.19,0:13:53.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The scum who ran away after tainting my sister and taking her savings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.09,0:13:54.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Please contact me if you spot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.81,0:14:07.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay to be doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.43,0:14:10.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's easier to give birth than to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.47,0:14:12.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A Japanese idiom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:14.27,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently my mom used it quite often.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.71,0:14:16.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And what does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:19.21,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's better to take action than to overthink things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:20.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's so like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:25.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That secret base brought back memories, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.12,0:14:27.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So you were still using it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:29.91,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Actually I was planning to close it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.04,0:14:32.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:38.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're strong, Suou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.93,0:14:46.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I swore to protect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.88,0:14:49.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.48,0:14:50.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Suou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.84,0:14:53.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You said that the military took Tanya with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:56.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:14:58.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Suou, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.69,0:15:03.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:05.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Nika.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.64,0:15:06.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.08,0:15:08.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:17.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This is the witness report of the professor's kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.80,0:15:20.70,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Anonymous tip, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.70,0:15:23.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There seems to be many people who should've forgotten about the past that we missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:29.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Should I report it to Major Repnin?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.09,0:15:29.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No need.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:36.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He probably has his hands full with the training of the new monster he got yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.90,0:15:46.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They've started to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.74,0:15:48.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,All right, July.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:51.40,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move till I come to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:09.24,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,To think you'd arrive before the information trickled in...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.24,0:16:10.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You saved me quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:13.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're angry, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.33,0:16:14.78,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:16.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.55,0:16:19.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Then your picture will be all over the Internet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.07,0:16:23.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I arranged it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:25.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be in deep shit if I don't return!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:27.03,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.03,0:16:29.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shion Pavlichenko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:32.24,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hand over the meteor core.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:34.51,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Then I won't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:35.70,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:38.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Contractors are all liars!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.05,0:16:39.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You can't trust them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:41.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:42.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.70,0:16:45.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the meteor core?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:48.00,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No! What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.08,0:16:55.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Pervert! Moron! Molester! Lecher!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:56.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.27,0:16:58.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Shion?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:17:00.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you kill Papa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:03.27,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you kill Bella as well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:06.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,How can you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.18,0:17:07.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,do it that easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:08.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a human...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:11.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.64,0:17:14.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why you can kill people without blinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:18.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what being a rational contractor is about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:20.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Can you even feel pain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.80,0:17:23.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Do contractors lose even that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.09,0:17:25.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly are contractors?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.47,0:17:27.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What's so fun about being one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.39,0:17:29.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why are there people like you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.98,0:17:37.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:39.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Put your hands on the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.65,0:17:43.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You've caused us some trouble, Shion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.94,0:17:45.91,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:46.96,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take you under our protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.57,0:17:48.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:50.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You took Tanya...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:53.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:57.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be the one taking the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.54,0:18:00.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A contractor?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:01.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,To think he would just show himself like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:05.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.71,0:18:08.00,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get in the mood without an audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.39,0:18:09.50,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.18,0:18:18.51,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Mysterious, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:32.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.61,0:18:35.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Even though he tried to kill me just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.64,0:18:36.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.58,0:18:39.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The show starts now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.58,0:18:44.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,After them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.62,0:19:01.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A contractor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:03.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a friend of that guy just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:05.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.06,0:19:19.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of the rest, Youko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.45,0:19:26.45,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Let me down! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:31.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,When they find out that I'm not Shion...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:33.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.64,0:19:36.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This is the most rational decision in that situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:42.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A cigarette cannot go through a coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:44.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There's a hole in the coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:46.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The gimmick is that the hole opens and closes with a delicate spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.01,0:19:51.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's my remuneration.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:54.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I have to explain my tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.95,0:19:57.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's really painful for a magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.94,0:20:03.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But thanks to that, I can use real magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:11.75,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.34,0:20:20.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run away by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:22.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.34,0:20:25.50,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Putting someone in a box and then piercing it with a saber...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.50,0:20:27.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There are several ways to do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.71,0:20:30.72,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,but the places the saber will pierce are planned beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.72,0:20:34.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If you adjust your body properly, you can avoid getting stabbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.73,0:20:46.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I told you. I'm a magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:47.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There're no tricks or gimmicks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.66,0:20:52.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He's distorting the space surrounding him, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:55.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore neither swords nor bullets will harm him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.82,0:21:00.30,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Distraction?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.60,0:21:12.20,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of attacking him with the knife, he went for the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:13.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.67,0:21:15.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hazuki-san, we're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.00,0:21:25.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.00,0:21:49.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hei...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.69,0:21:52.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't, Yin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.97,0:21:57.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.20,0:22:19.70,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Kureteku yuubae ni senaka osarete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.20,0:22:19.70,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}My back is pressed by the darkening glow of dusk
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.86,0:22:30.21,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Arukidasu kage ga shimesu hou e
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.86,0:22:30.21,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I start walking toward where my shadow points
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.21,0:22:39.77,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Taenai ikutsu mo no deai to wakare o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.21,0:22:39.77,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Repeating the many, ceaseless encounters and partings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.90,0:22:45.95,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Kurikaeshi doko e mukau no ka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.90,0:22:45.95,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Where do I head to?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.70,0:22:51.05,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Hito wa dare mo mayoinagara
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.70,0:22:51.05,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}For all people, while they are lost,
Dialogue: 2,0:22:50.68,0:22:55.81,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}tsumi to iu na no sadame o seotte
Dialogue: 2,0:22:50.68,0:22:55.81,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}they bear the fate known as sin
Dialogue: 3,0:22:55.58,0:23:04.46,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Sore de mo nao ikiru imi o shiru darou
Dialogue: 3,0:22:55.58,0:23:04.46,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Nevertheless, I'll still learn of the meaning to live, right?
Dialogue: 4,0:23:04.28,0:23:09.55,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Bokura wa sou Day by Day
Dialogue: 4,0:23:04.28,0:23:09.55,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}That's right, Day by Day,
Dialogue: 5,0:23:09.29,0:23:16.50,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ashita e tsuzuku michi no tochuu de
Dialogue: 5,0:23:09.29,0:23:16.50,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}we're midway on the road leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 6,0:23:16.13,0:23:24.09,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Now Say It Again kimi to futari no mama
Dialogue: 6,0:23:16.13,0:23:24.09,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Now Say It Again, though it'd be great if
Dialogue: 7,0:23:24.01,0:23:34.38,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}irareta nara ii no ni naa...
Dialogue: 7,0:23:24.01,0:23:34.38,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I could remain together with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.87,0:23:51.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,BK201 has...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.76,0:23:54.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.06,0:24:01.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's the terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.32,0:24:03.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The place where everything ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.89,0:24:07.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The white snowfield is drenched with blood and gunsmoke,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.22,0:24:10.15,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,and the decay of their first love drifts into the hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.70,0:24:11.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The scream,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.20,0:24:14.70,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,the invocation, an uninvited spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.94,0:24:17.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,When you wake up, the Grim Reaper drifts away with your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.56,0:24:20.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.77,0:24:23.24,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's the turning point of fates.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.97,0:24:25.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.39,0:24:28.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,a light was set free.